name: DevilHS Artstyle LoRA
description:
This is my DevilHS Artstyle LoRA. I liked the way DevilHS draws things, and I'm a general fan of more western/comic style art.

The strength is good for 0.6 to 0.8, but I use 0.75 strength.

All images generated on my custom blends. I used Hires fix with the orangemix VAE.

I also have a Discord. Join if you wanna share results, get advice, or make requests.

Update: Archiving these LoRAs. Though I don't believe it is entirely wrong to copy an artstyle (I use these artstyle LoRAs to make my mixes), I never did ask for permission and honestly, most artists wouldn't say yes.
